				<div class="bible-name">The Holy Bible â€“ Knox Translation</div>
				<div class="book-name">The Book of Wisdom </div>
				<div class="act-chapter">
					<div class="prev-chapter"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20200203103029/http://catholicbible.online/knox/OT/Wis/7568">&lt; prev</a></div>|
					<div class="chapter">Chapter 16</div>
